3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's focus on online learning and optimization is closely related to artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper's analysis of the dynamic regret of online learning involves the use of algorithms and data structures.
